}{FFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF}{GGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGGG,HHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH,IIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIIII,JJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJJ}
